author: EducatorLife85
text: What if rest, stillness, and slowness are the real bags?!  And we've been deceived all these years to think degrees, money, and accolades were the bags!...Something to ponder.

author: EducatorLife85
text: Going into 2021, we must unlearn the things that have kept us stagnant and not evolving!  The new calendar year presents us with the opportunity to do a hard reset in our lives. We must re-examine, readjust, and realign. We must persevere to become our highest selves.

author: EducatorLife85
text: As 2020 comes to a close, education professionals must re-examine what is most important, instructionally and holistically!  What does success truly look like at the K-12 and college levels?  How has this pandemic created a heightened sense of reality and new sense of urgency?
